---
import DonateButton from "./DonateButton.astro";
---
<section id="support" class="section bg-sand scroll-mt-20 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 paper-noise opacity-50"></div>

  <div class="container-x relative">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-lava mb-4">For funders</p>
      <h2 class="text-display-md leading-[1.05] text-ink" style="text-wrap: balance;">
        If you fund work like this,<br/>
        <span class="italic text-lava">come talk to us.</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-8 text-stone text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-5 max-w-prose">
        <p>
          We’re a Hawai‘i 501(c)(3) supporting the people who run mobile food businesses
          across the islands. Right now that’s a long-form podcast spotlighting their work,
          a marketing curriculum being built for the next pilot cohort, and ongoing
          advocacy with state and county regulators on the rules that hit small operators
          hardest.
        </p>
        <p>
          Where money goes: episode production, course materials and instructor stipends,
          legal review for the advocacy work, and the basics of running a small foundation
          out of a PO box on Hawai‘i Island. We publish what we spend.
        </p>
        <p class="text-ink">
          If you fund storytelling, small-business support, or food-system work in
          Hawai‘i — we’d like to hear from you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
        <a href="mailto:hello@hawaiimobilefoodfoundation.org?subject=HMFF%20funding%20inquiry"
           class="btn btn-donor">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="3" y="5" width="14" height="11" rx="2"/>
            <path d="m3 7 7 5 7-5"/>
          </svg>
          hello@hawaiimobilefoodfoundation.org
        </a>
        <DonateButton label="Or donate directly" />
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-stone">
        EIN forthcoming · 501(c)(3) confirmed · Receipts via Stripe
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
